componentDescription: An unstyled select item to be used within a Select.

closeOnClick.description: If true, the select will close when the select item is clicked.

disabled.description: If true, the select item will be disabled.

id.description: The id of the select item.

label.description: A text representation of the select item's content. Used for keyboard text navigation matching.

onClick.description: The click handler for the select item.

value.description: The value of the select item.
